$ VBA: function and sub parameters

  → development/languages/VBA/language/subs-and-functions/optional-parameters[Optional parameters]

  The optional declaration of a parameter with → development/languages/VBA/language/subs-and-functions/byVal-byRef[`byVal` or `byRef`] allows to pass a parameter
 *by reference* or as *copied value*.

  The → development/languages/VBA/language/subs-and-functions/parameters/paramArray[`paramArray`] keyword allows to
  pass an arbitrary number of arguments to a sub or function.


